            "id": 3906,
            "user": {
                "id": 90,
                "name": "Saukko"
            },
            "notes": "I think it is disadvantageous for a soldier to have only one weapon to shoot with. I think the best solution would be that telecting two MP40s/Thompsons would be restricted and you would be just able to pick MP40 as primary and pistol or two as secondary.\r\n\r\nOtherwise the message is now fixed but I don't keep this as a permanent solution.\r\n\r\n-*S",
            "created_on": "2014-11-28T12:27:16Z",
